reviewText: Any video where the emcee is using a bull-horn ("come out with your hands up") is bordering on the really bad. Combine it with "contests" staged in the parking lot of a strip club (I see though why they were using the bullhorn, fast get-away if the cops care enough to show up) yeah, totally bad, and not in the good sense. Topless yes, bottom-less some, pretty crappy overall. Don't know about parts One or Two, I assume it's the same stuff, different night perhaps?
